'''Pit Bull''' was a pair of [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvettes]] belonging to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. One of them contained armaments the other contained generators. They arrived at the ''[[Mayhem]]''{{'s}} location when the ''Mayhem'' failed to stop rebels from liberating [[Habassa]]n [[Slavery/Legends|slaves]].

